headline: Citigroup Maintains Buy on Weyerhaeuser, Raises Price Target to $32
summary: Citigroup  analyst Anthony Pettinari   maintains Weyerhaeuser (NYSE:WY) with a Buy and raises the price target from $30 to $32.

headline: Weyerhaeuser Company Declares Dividend on Common Shares
summary: Weyerhaeuser Company (NYSE: WY) today announced that its board of directors declared a quarterly base cash dividend of $0.21 per share on the common stock of the company, payable in cash on March 20, 2026, to holders of record of such common stock as of the close of business on March 10, 2026.
